divs: sighting detailsgoing to work on 9\29\12 i observed a large glowing all white very oblong object in the sky about 40 ft above ground traveling at a speed higher than a jet would be traveling.it vanished behind a warehouse in a desending pace & never re-appeared.by this time i stop my vehicle & was outside watching this aprox. 30 seconds later a second object appeared from the same direction as the 1st & desended in the same direction.the 2nd object was identical as the 1st one.there was no flashing lights or sound coming fron either object the whie light was very bright & i could not make any identifications on either object. there is a comercial airport aprox 2 mi away but these objects where not traveling in a normal flight pattern for a aircraft to land there & they were way to low at that distance freom the airport to be plausible.after work i did spend probably an hour looking for they could have landed
